In small bowl, combine dressing and lime juice; set aside. Divide arugula evenly between 4 salad plates. Cut avocados in half lengthwise, remove seed and peel. Cut each avocado half into 5 slices. Place 5 slices of avocado, in a fan shape, over each plate of arugula. Place grapefruit sections on each slice of avocado; top with red onion. Drizzle each salad with dressing mixture and sprinkle with pepper.